T1  - Objective and Social Factors as Determinants of Task Perceptions and Responses: An Integrated Perspective and Empirical Investigation
AU  - Griffin, Ricky W.
AU  - Bateman, Thomas S.
AU  - Wayne, Sandy J.
AU  - Head, Thomas C.
Y1  - 1987/09/01
